spec: agent-core.ai-docs/v1
namespace: "Contract\\Hook"
fqcn: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Contract\\Hook"
updatedAt: 2026-04-22
description: "Hook interfaces for intercepting agent loop lifecycle: context transforms, LLM conversion, tool call boundaries, cancellation, and message providers."
files[7]{file,type,summary}:
  BeforeProviderRequestHookInterface.php,interface,"Intercepts provider requests before dispatch, allowing modification or cancellation."
  CancellationTokenInterface.php,interface,Signals cooperative cancellation for long-running or asynchronous hook operations.
  ConvertToLlmHookInterface.php,interface,Converts raw message arrays into a structured MessageBag for LLM consumption.
  FollowUpMessagesProviderInterface.php,interface,Supplies contextual follow-up messages based on current agent state.
  NullCancellationToken.php,readonly final class,Non-cancelable sentinel implementing the cancellation token contract for scenarios that do not require abort support.
  SteeringMessagesProviderInterface.php,interface,Supplies steering messages that configure or route agent behavior.
  TransformContextHookInterface.php,interface,Transforms message payloads in the agent loop with optional cancellation support.